OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine. Widely warm and humid with
OL,7,Flight winds, although cooler along
OL,8,Fcoastal areas as the breeze freshens
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBecoming cloudier from the
OL,12,Fwest as a band of heavy, perhaps
OL,13,Fthundery, showers moves east during
OL,14,Fthe evening. Drier with clearer spells
OL,15,Fduring the later part of the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FFine with further sunshine,
OL,18,Ftemperatures continuing to increase to
OL,19,Fbecome hot. A warm and humid night to
OL,20,Ffollow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
